text: Mix veg rice very good. The fellas are nice, friendly and courteous. Price reasonable and portion is good. Must try when here.
I like the mix rice here. Always good taste.

Couldn't find SaveurThai on googlemaps at this location hence posting my review here. This is their 6th outlet apparently and the food is so good. Ordered 7 dishes and the bill came up to $60ish, which is much cheaper than a typical zhu chao place.
One thing to note though, perharps because it's relatively new, there was only 2 staff working of which 1 had to work as a cashier too. Be patient to wait for their food, you would not regret it!
Food is nice but the washroom is insanely filled with cigarette smoke smell by diners, walked in and had an old man walking out with a ciggie in his mouth. Horrible.
The Vegetarian Food is tasty, not too oily nor laden with MSG and reasonably priced !
